      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i tried a log transform but the residuals still look pretty messy, just less extreme. i suspect there might be some specific outliers causing most of the skew. do you think i should just prune those out, or is there a specific way to test if they're actually valid data points versus just noise?",
